# Ignore everything by default
*

# Keep gitignore
!.gitignore

# Allow only these two projects
!hub_firmware/
!hub_firmware/glazia_hub/
!hub_firmware/glazia_hub/**

!sensor_firmware/
!sensor_firmware/glazia_sensor/
!sensor_firmware/glazia_sensor/**

# Never track docs/agent/code clutter
*.md
**/*.md
**/AGENTS.md
**/CLAUDE.md
**/.claude/
**/.code/
**/.codecov.yml

# Build/cache junk
**/build/
**/__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
.DS_Store
.vscode/
.idea/
.venv/
venv/
